This allows lazy creation of tokens or       creating NFTs by setting the id's high bits with the method       described in ERC1155 or to use ids representing values other than       successive small integers. If you wish to create ids as successive       small integers you can either subclass this class to count onchain       or maintain the offchain cache of identifiers recommended in       ERC1155 and calculate successive ids from that.
